
# What Weâ€™re Building

## The Outside Inn

A virtual destination where:

* Outsiders are welcomed to step Innside, and stay.
* A growing community of Innsiders earns rewards for early patronage.
* The brand explores the threshold between polarities.

---

# Gaming Livestream

* E.I. Werner will stream a variety of games on a consistent schedule.
* Streams will be simulcast across:

  * Facebook
  * Kick
  * Rumble
  * Twitch
  * YouTube
* Proprietary Outside Inn music plays at approximately 50% volume during streams.

---

# Innspired LoFi Radio Station (24/7)

* A 24/7 LoFi fantasy radio stream broadcast across strategic platforms.
* Music composed by Carson Thatcher will loop over an animation created by Marwan Hasnaoui.
* The animation features **Holdt**, a steampunk Holden Caulfield, writing in focused contentment.
* Radio music continues at lower volume during live gaming streams.

---

# Material Products

* Collectible posters, coasters, stickers, and vinyl records.
* Includes both standard and limited-edition variants.

---

# Digital Products

* Mint packages of art as NFTs on the blockchain.
* NFTs linked to exclusive online and real-life rewards.

---

# Brand: The Threshold Between Polarity

The Outside Inn is built on the concept of boundaries and the space between them.

### Polarity Table (from page 2)

| Inside            | Outside        | Between          |
| ----------------- | -------------- | ---------------- |
| Home              | Destination    | Inn              |
| Indoors           | Outdoors       | Window           |
| Rye field playing | Death by cliff | Holden Caulfield |
| Joy               | Danger         | Precipice        |
| Artifact          | Machine        | Artifice         |
| Welcome           | Unwelcome      | Invitation       |
| Civilization      | Wilderness     | Gate             |
| Locked            | Unlocked       | Key              |
| Inhale            | Exhale         | Breath           |
| Earth             | Heavens        | Sky              |
| History           | Fantasy        | Myth             |

| Inside  | Outside | Between |
| ------- | ------- | ------- |
| Mortal  | Divine  | Legend  |
| Day     | Night   | Dusk    |
| Night   | Day     | Dawn    |
| Past    | Present | Memory  |
| Present | Future  | Dream   |
| Solid   | Liquid  | Magma   |
| Liquid  | Solid   | Steam   |
